Questioned Central BJP govtтАЩs sincerity in reviving BSNL. Criticised the Central govt for expecting BSNL to compete with 5G technology of JIO & Airtel, with their old 2G & 3G technology. Demanded that BSNL, being a PSU, should be given 5G spectrum free of cost by Govt of India.
